data.description: Ideal location in the Bonnie Brae Section of Lockport. Easy access to Shopping and Highway 355. Second largest lot in the development at 11,000 plus feet. A 3 plus garage, that can actually park 4 cars (with one sideways in the rear). An additional shed behind the garage. There is no shortage on storage! The home is a solidly maintained home with all mechanicals working. Solid bones, so bring your ideas for the interior. Living room does offer a Fireplace. See it today.
